 <table width=100% cellpadding=10>
 <tr><td>
<div align="center" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
</div>
<table>
<tr><td align=right>Issue:</td><td><b>Issue 22, June 2003</b></td></tr>
<tr><td align=right>Section:</td><td><b>Interviews</b></td></tr>
<tr><td align=right>Author:</td><td><b><span class="missing">Sonic</span></b></td></tr>
</table>
<p>
<table border=0 cellpadding=15><tr><td>
<table border=5 cellpadding=15><tr><td BGCOLOR=black>
<div align="center"><font color="white" style="font-size: 18px;"><b>Finally! What you've all been waiting for.
<br>
An interview with the basilisk! (If a very quick one!)</b></div>
<br>
By Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font>.</font>
<br><br>
<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 20px;">
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">I've always wanted to interview you, Mr. Bas, old buddy
old pal; there are so many questions I'd like to ask you. But I'll start off
by introducing myself ...</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> exclaims "</font><font color="#FCFC54">I'm Sonic, I've been playing since 1999, I'm blue,
with spiky hair etc, I'm sure you've heard of me!</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Yes, I've heard of you Sonic, you're that ugly one who
always steals things from my house!</font><font color="#A85400"></font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Yes ... That would be the one, I'm sure.</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> asks "</font><font color="#FCFC54">So ... I'd like to ask you, what is your first name Mr.
Basilisk?</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Well, you're getting it all wrong, first name Bas, second
name, Ilisk. People have been getting my name wrong since the beginning!</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> asks "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Oh right, sorry B, it's ok if I call you B isn't it?</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk groans "</font><font color="#FCFC54">I suppose so</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Ok! On to my next question, how did you actually get so
ugly? (No offence B, but you must admit, you are quite horrendous!)</font><font
color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk <font color="#FCFC54">grimaces.</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Hmm ... I can't quite remember the exact date, but it
was long, long ago. Back before you were around, sonny. I was minding my
own business, trotting around my house endlessly (as usual) when I heard
a key grate in the lock and the front door swing right open!
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">The rays of sunlight beamed through the door onto my
face, not being used to the sunlight as I'd never left my cosy 6 rooms
before, I was sunburned very badly on my face, and my skin is always dry
and flaky now! If only there was some Nivea skin moisturizer in MUD2!</font><font
color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> asks "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Oh dear ... That sounds quite terrible, and what exactly
are you doing, living in a clock all by yourself?</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk replies "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Well, that's none of your business is it really?!</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Touchy! Please, let's keep the peace just this
once for the interview, fans of Muddled Times all over The Land will be
reading this!</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk exclaims "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Hmm. Ok, but next time you see me it won't be pretty!</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk <font color="#FCFC54">chuckles.</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Saying that, I seem to have run out of questions! How
unfortunate <G>.</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Thank god for that, you were beginning to annoy me!</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> exclaims "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Oi! Watch it!</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">Sonic the <font color="#5454fc">blue</font> says "</font><font color="#FCFC54">Well, I'll leave it at that. See you around B! (erm, wait
a minute, no I won't!).</font><font color="#A85400">".</font>
<br>
<font color="#A85400">The basilisk <font color="#FCFC54">waves.</font>
</div>
</td></tr></table>
</td></tr></table>
